description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Waikiki Beach & Diamond Head / Oahu
-View from the top of Diamond Head / Oahu
-Sunset view of Hawaii Island
-Hanauma Bay / Oahu

-Kualoa Beach / Oahu
-Sea turtles at Laniakea Beach / Oahu
-King Kamehameha Statue / Oahu
-Waikiki Beach / Oahu
-Kalakaua Avenue / Oahu
name: Hawaii - Most beautiful places in the World -
